Project Description:

Making an app where a user can enter ingredients they have to retrieve recipes that can be made with said ingredients., Favorite the ingredients , mark favorite recipes 

User story:
I am wanna be home chef and I have ingredients that I have no idea what do with- this app will assist with finding recipe ideas.

